name: 64 Test Map
description: This is a map that is exclusive to Doom 64 EX (it can be only played with 64 EX). Made by the Doom Builder 64 (2 originally). It is a test map, but I figured about publishing it. READ THIS TO RUN THE MAP: 1- Put it in your Doom 64EX folder. 2- Open the launcher and type at the bottom: -file 64ways.wad
